OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHow to keep animals cool in
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthe hot weather            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, With the UK in the grips of a heatwave,
OL,6, it's not just humans who are trying to 
OL,7, keep cool, it's also important for     
OL,8, animals and pets to escape the         
OL,9, excessive heat. Here are just some of  
OL,10, the ways our furry friends have been   
OL,11, trying to cool down.                   
OL,13,FTo keep pets safe in the heat, the     
OL,14,FRSPCA says they need constant access to
OL,15,Ffresh water. Ice cubes can be put in   
OL,16,Ftheir water bowl or you could make some
OL,17,Ffrozen pet-friendly treats.            
OL,19,FOr give them damp towels to lie on.    
